commit message: Fix for #5 'Wrong charset in serbian translations'
k3b-geoHelper: Added Improvements from https://github.com/k3b/APhotoManager/ : support for uri-schema geoarea:{lat},{lon},{lat},{lon}, slf4j-support,
Refactored app-independant GuestureOverlay, OverlayDebug, ZoomUtil into seperate namespace de.k3b.android.osmdroid

added support for wikimedia-api-xml (i.e. wikipedia or wikivoyage)

Example
https://de.wikivoyage.org/w/api.php?action=query&format=xml&prop=coordinates|info|pageimages&inprop=url&piprop=thumbnail&generator=geosearch&ggscoord=28.12722|-15.43139&ggsradius=10000&ggslimit=5&pilimit=5
added inference symbol from and link from
Implemented infering href=link src=symbol from description to handle kml from https://tools.wmflabs.org/kmlexport/?article=Category:Gran_Canaria&linksfrom=1&l=3
replaced local sourcecode of OSMBonusPack+k3b-geoHelper with latest com.github.MKergall.osmbonuspack:OSMBonusPack:v5.6 and com.github.k3b:k3b-geoHelper:v1.1.3
added geo as an optional submodule for k3b-geoHelper
